Fall_River.Squire William B. Canedy House: The Squire William B. Canedy House is a historic house at 2634 N. Main Street in Fall River, Massachusetts. It is a 2-1/2 story wood frame structure, five bays wide, with a side-gable roof, twin end chimneys, and wooden shingle siding. The center entrance is flanked by sidelight windows and pilasters, and is topped by a semi-elliptical solid fan.
